column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_i, p.cModelMag_g, p.cModelMag_i, p.cModelMagErr_g, p.cModelMagErr_i, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_i, expAB_g FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
